Permutations for Java

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Lists
    This class contains immutable array based implementations of List that have efficient indexOf, lastIndexOf and contains methods.

    A permutation that can be used to rearrange arrays.

    This class contains the sort and from factory methods.
